    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-01-05T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-01-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="645" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d645">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Taylor</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-01-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 5,
                                1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your telegram of 4th opportune. Friendly disposition manifested by
                            Spanish Government appreciated.</p>
                <p>So long as Spain accords most-favored-nation treatment to American
                            products President will refrain from exercising power of discrimination
                            or exclusion against Spanish products. Read this to minister for foreign
                            affairs.</p>
            </div>
